error.message:
The provider settings validation operation has failed with code 'SapHanaConnectionFailed'.
      Possible Causes: The operation failed with error: 'Connection to SAP HANA Failed, Error Text:  Error(-10709, "Connection failed (RTE:[89006] System call 'connect' failed, rc=111:Connection refused {169.254.254.5:41926 -> 10.0.81.4:30013} (169.254.254.5:41926 -> 10.0.81.4:30013))")'.
      Recommended Action: 'Please check if the instance number is correct. For more details on the error, please refer: https://userapps.support.sap.com/sap/support/knowledge/en/2213725'.

The provider settings validation operation has failed with code 'SOAPApiConnectionError'.
      Possible Causes: The operation failed with error: 'Unable to reach the hostname: 10.0.82.4 with the input provided.'.
      Recommended Action: 'Please check the input hostname, instance number, and host file entries. Refer point k from the link: https://aka.ms/AmsNwHostfileEntry'.
